Package: microData
Title: World Bank Microdata Assistant
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Gutama Girja", "Urago", , "girjagutama@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5588-2301"))
Description: This package helps to read worldbank microdata files and 
    organize them with excel. The work flow is starting with `dictionary()`
    function tho extract variables and their description form the web, followed
    by `add_sheet()` to the new table an existing excel work book. Finally, using 
    `micro_csv()` to read local data and apply attributes from the excel workbook.
